2024

- 39 goals (led team), 17 assists, 56 points over 15 starts

2023

- 51 goals (9th all-time), 17 assists, 68 points over 19 games (18 starts)

- 24 draw controls, 11 ground balls, 10 caused turnovers, 3 game-winning goals

- Season Highs: 6 goals (4/15 vs. Bridgeport), 3 assists (4/2 vs. Post), 9 points (4/2 vs. Post), 2 caused turnovers (4/22 at Felician), 2 ground balls (5/7 vs. Dominican), 4 draw controls (4/2 vs. Post)

2022

- 46 goals (led team), 3 assists, 49 points over 15 games (14 starts)

- 14 ground balls, 11 caused turnovers, 3 draw controls

- Season Highs: 6 goals (twice), 7 points (3/18 at Chestnut Hill), 3 caused turnovers (3/26 vs. Nyack), 4 ground balls (3/30 vs. Chestnut Hill), 2 draw controls (4/2 at Caldwell)

- CACC Stats: 10th in goals

- 2x CACC Honor Roll

2021

- 12 games, 7 starts, 16 goals, 2 assists, 18 points

- 13 ground balls, 6 caused turnovers

- 1x CACC Rookie of the Week

Background

- Played field hockey, basketball, and lacrosse at Lower Cape May Regional High School

- Named First Team CAL All-Star in lacrosse her junior year

Personal

- Daughter of Jeffrey and Denise

- Has three siblings: Giana, Ciara, and Giordana
